text: José Jacinto Hidalgo was a sprinter from Venezuela. Hidalgo competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics. He was born on 4 January 1943 and died on 22 May 2020.José Jacinto Hidalgo == References == Category:1943 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Venezuelan sprinters Category:Hurdlers Category:Olympians for Venezuela
